[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

[[include :scp-wiki:component:author-label-source start=--
|name=the One and Only
|no-right-margin=*]]
To see more of my works, check out the page you are literally looking at right now.
[[include :scp-wiki:component:author-label-source end=--]]

[[div class="publicaff_memo"]]
[[module ListUsers users="."]]
**%%title%%, the following message requires your urgent attention.**
[[/module]]
**You have been granted special clearance to access the following file for your reading eyes only. By the authority of the Internal Arbitration Bureau, this file is 4/8350 classified.**
[[<]]
[[module ListPages name="scp-8350" limit="1"]]
[[div class="feature {$background}"]]
[[size 150%]]**%%title_linked%%**[[/size]]@@  @@//Public Affairs//
 +**{{%%rating%%}}**@@  @@**(Latest Post)**
[[collapsible show="Commentary" hide="-"]]
##000|Hey, y'all! After surviving a year-long writing desert, I'm back with this. Whether you hate it or love it, I'm pretty damn happy with how it turned out. This is, by far, my longest article yet -- not too sure what happened there -- but it's certainly my best work (according to me, an unbiased source). For clarity, I know that on the surface, this article is a bit goofy and bordering on lolFoundation, but it also serves as an analogy for my own experiences with struggling socially and having a spontaneous outward impression arbitrarily influence people's perception of you. If you want more information about that, you can check out the article's discussion thread.##
[[/collapsible]] @@ @@
[[/div]]
[[/module]]
[[/<]]
**-- //Bob Humanman, Director of the Public Affairs Department//**
[[/div]]

